      "recording_id": "13ad68c9-f604-42bd-a5e7-b34890d28ab5",
      "end_time": 72.9,
      "start_time": 61.66,
      "recording_attendee_id": "ad0221b7-c5c4-4cca-8f43-34b028d2cfba",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "I'm doing good, I'm doing good. Thanks for asking. Um Hey, I was on your guys website um and saw that you guys are opening up in the spring of two thousand and twenty-one I wanted"
